  <name>Time Limit</name>
  <summary>A simple and beautiful timer</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Drag the blue arrow to set a timer. Release to start and click to pause. When the time is up, a notification will show up with a nice sound.</p>
    <p>Keyboard shortcuts:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <code>Space</code>
        for pause/play
      </li>
      <li>
        <code>Esc</code>
        to reset
      </li>
    </ul>
  </description>
